TITLE: Installing Dependencies for Leaflet.MarkerCluster Development
DESCRIPTION: Commands for installing the necessary dependencies before building the project. Requires npm to install jake globally and local dependencies.
SOURCE: https://github.com/leaflet/leaflet.markercluster/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
npm install -g jake
npm install
```

