TITLE: Building Leaflet.MarkerCluster
DESCRIPTION: Command to build the Leaflet.MarkerCluster project using jake. The compiled output will be placed in the dist/ directory.
SOURCE: https://github.com/leaflet/leaflet.markercluster/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
jake
```

