TITLE: Running Unit Tests for Leaflet.MarkerCluster
DESCRIPTION: Command to execute the unit tests for the Leaflet.MarkerCluster project using jake.
SOURCE: https://github.com/leaflet/leaflet.markercluster/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
jake test
```

